
Key Highlights:

1️⃣ Location Premiums

Palm Jumeirah commands 35% higher price/sqft than market average

Dubai Marina vs International City: 180% price difference for similar properties

Top premium areas: Palm Jumeirah, Downtown Dubai, Dubai Marina

2️⃣ Amenity Impact

Beach access adds AED 500,000 (~22% price increase)

Pool adds AED 300,000 (~13%), Gym adds AED 100,000 (~4%)

Metro proximity boosts price by 15%

3️⃣ Investment Intelligence

45 properties identified as Grade A investments

Best ROI areas: Jumeirah Village Circle (8.2%), Dubai Hills (7.5%)

Undervalued gems: high-amenity properties priced below area average

4️⃣ Market Efficiency Findings

Beach properties sell 42 vs 68 days (26 days faster)

Luxury amenities reduce selling time by 34%

Professional photos show no ROI

5️⃣ Predictive Modeling

Top price drivers: Size (32%), Beach access (28%), Location (22%)

ML predicts within AED 280,000 of actual price

Luxury score explains 41% of price variation

6️⃣ Statistical Significance

✅ Significant: Beach access, Size, Location (p < 0.001)

❌ Not significant: Professional photos, Gym alone (p > 0.05)

⚠️ Moderate: Pool, Metro proximity (p < 0.10)

Business Recommendations:

Investors: Target JVC & Dubai Hills for best rental yields

Sellers: Highlight beach access (cuts selling time by ~38%)

Developers: Add pools over gyms (higher ROI)

Agents: Skip professional photos (no price impact)

Banks: Metro proximity = lower risk (faster sales)
